title: Sarah Wilson Photography - Des Moines, IA
description: As a proud Des Moines native and passionate photographer, I specialize in capturing the genuine and authentic moments that define life's most significant chapters. Whether you're embarking on the exciting journey of high school seniorhood, expecting the pitter-patter of tiny feet, or celebrating the love that binds us together, I'm here to turn your stories into timeless images.
author: Sarah Wilson Photography
